Package org.motechproject.mots.web

Class LocationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.motechproject.mots.web.BaseController
      • org.motechproject.mots.web.LocationController
  • @Controller
public class LocationController
extends BaseController
    This class is responsible manage and manipulate entity classes related to location (i.e. Sector, Facility, District, Village).
